Question 1.Explanation:
A = ₦5,500 = I + P ------ (1)

T = 5 years

P = ?

I = PRT/100 ----- (2)

From (1)

I = 5,500 – P

Equating (1) and (2), we have

5,500 – P = PRT/100

5,500 – P = P(2)(5)/100

(5,500 – P) = 10P/100

(5,000 – P) 10 = P

55,000 – 10P = P

55,000 = 11P

11P = 55,000

P = 55,000/11

P = N5,000
